description: OFFER DEADLINE TUES 3/5 by 12pm! A true home in South Boston. Each space in this East Side single family has been lovingly & intentionally renovated to truly shine while still preserving the charm. A modest exterior gives way to soaring ceilings & original hardwood floors. Front facing welcoming living room w large windows. Open dining room leads into custom designed, stunning "Earl Gray" kitchen. Kitchen gleams in SW exposure with floor to ceiling built-in cabinetry, DW, pantry & also features Liebherr fridge, custom vent hood, Thermador gas range, custom pullouts, brass bistro shelves, & Schoolhouse Electric lighting. Entertaining made easy w direct access to deck & brick patio from dining room. Bold powder room completes first floor. Upstairs boasts three sizable bedrooms. Front facing bedroom accommodates king bed. Full bathroom with modern finishes and custom vanity with Carrara countertop. Home is well positioned to access conveniences, beach, public transport, restaurants.
